DE_Stability - International Crisis

Iranian Terrorists are attemping to blow
up weapons stored in an Iranian college campus.
Help keep the region stable.
 
Counter-Terrorists: Enter the storage facility at 
the college campus and keep the terrorists from
detonating the explosives.

Terrorists: Blow up the storage depots in the 
campus.
 
Other Notes: There are two bomb sites. Map is intended for small-scale, fast, tactical gameplay.
